\f0\fs24 \cf0 # Create\'ae 3 Wall Following and Door Detection Robot\
\
This project implements a wall-following robot using the iRobot Create\'ae 3 platform. The robot follows walls using PID control, detects doors based on collisions, and switches sides to continue wall following on the opposite wall after certain conditions are met. The robot stops after completing wall following on both sides.\
